a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fwho-owns-trump-coin-whales-retail-investors-buy-meme-token-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ememes%20rallied%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20did%20the%20%24SOL%20token.%20It's%20price%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20%24294%20on%20Sunday%20and%20witnessed%20over%20%2450%20billion%20in%20trading%20volume%20that%20weekend%2C%20according%20to%20Bernstein.%20Since%20the%20token%20is%20used%20to%20pay%20fees%20related%20to%20other%20coins%20issued%20on%20the%20Solana%20blockchain%2C%20demand%20for%20%24SOL%20surged%20aggressively.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20so%20high%20that%20it%20sparked%20outages%20at%20one%20of%20the%20top%20crypto%20exchanges%2C%20Coinbase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20clear%20we%20need%20to%20step%20up%20our%20game%20on%20Solana%2C%20scale%20our%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20provide%20native%20support%20for%20common%20use%20cases%20like%20DEX%2Fmemecoin%20trading%2C%26quot%3B%20Coinbase%20CEO%20Brian%20Armstrong%20wrote%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fbrian_armstrong%2Fstatus%2F1881987902701207678%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chart%20showing%20solana%20trading%20volume%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f36b196626c40984f948%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221624%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%2C%20January%2020th%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20more%20use%20cases%20like%20this%20could%20be%20coming%2C%20crypto%20analysts%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-crypto-industry-donald-trump-election-reserve-regulation-sec-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epro-crypto%20regulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20expected%20under%20President%20Trump%2C%20meme%20coins%20could%20proliferate%20in%20a%20n