lysts%20have%20blamed%20several%20factors.%20The%20luxury%20sector%20fell%20overall%20in%202024%2C%20with%20industry%20bellwethers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flvmh-luxury-louis-vuitton-struggles-china-slowdown-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELVMH%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Kering%20also%20tumbling.%20In%20October%2C%20Wells%20Fargo%20downgraded%20Canada%20Goose's%20stock%20to%20%26quot%3Bunderweight%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20a%20lackluster%20performance%20on%20social%20media%20and%20overreliance%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhats-behind-china-luxury-goods-slowdown-economy-changing-consumer-tastes-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20it%20has%20the%20most%20retail%20stores%20and%20which%20produces%20the%20most%20revenue%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20facing%20economic%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202023%2C%20Canada%20Goose%20released%20a%20strategic%20plan%20that%20included%20three%20focus%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20accelerating%20growth%20among%20women%20and%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20building%20its%20direct-to-consumer%20network%2C%20and%20creating%20new%20products%20while%20expanding%20existing%20categories.%20The%20goal%20is%20for%20revenue%20to%20hit%20%242.1%20billion%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20a%20wholesale%20brand%20for%20so%20long%2C%20and%20we%20decided%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20have%20direct%20relationships%20with%20our%20consumers.%20We%20wanted%20to%20sell%20online%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20have%20stores%2C%26quot%3B%20Reiss%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canada%20goose%20store%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792a9ca2fcded5e907486c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECanada%20Goose%20is%20expanding%20its%20direct-to-consumer%20channels%2C%20including%20by%20opening%20more%20retail