rs%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20diversification%20attempts%20have%20been%20mixed.%20Sales%20of%20non-heavyweight-down%20units%20%E2%80%94%20including%20apparel%2C%20wind%20wear%2C%20and%20footwear%20%E2%80%94%20were%20up%2020%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%202025%20fiscal%20year%20and%20made%20up%2046%25%20of%20sales%20in%20fiscal%202024.%20(The%20move%20away%20from%20down%20is%20also%20a%20win%20for%20PETA%2C%20which%20has%20protested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-goose-jackets-fur-free-by-the-end-of-2022-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanada%20Goose's%20use%20of%20fur%20and%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20stopped%20using%20fur%20in%202022.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20Canada%20Goose%20still%20leans%20heavily%20on%20its%20signature%20item%3B%20for%20the%202024%20fiscal%20year%2C%20nearly%2080%25%20of%20its%20annual%20EBITDA%20came%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20which%20ends%20in%20December%2C%20when%20customers%20are%20shelling%20out%20on%20thick%20winter%20jackets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20other%20luxury%20outerwear%20brands%2C%20like%20Moncler%2C%20collaborations%20have%20been%20one%20way%20to%20attract%20repeat%20customers.%20Canada%20Goose%20is%20attempting%20something%20similar%20by%20appointing%20Haider%20Ackermann%2C%20the%20French%20fashion%20designer%20who%20also%20heads%20design%20at%20Tom%20Ford%2C%20as%20creative%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20collection%2C%20released%20in%20November%2C%20achieved%20%26quot%3Brecord-setting%20marketing%20success%2C%20and%20his%20new%20capsule%20collection%2C%20Snow%20Goose%20by%20Canada%20Goose%2C%20has%20been%20exceptionally%20well-received%20by%20consumers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Canada%20Goose%20spokesperson%20said%2C%20though%20did%20not%20provide%20sales%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAchieving%20luxury%20is%20one%20thing.%20Maintaining%20growth%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20though%2C%20may%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20wild%20goose%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-goose-status-symbol-outerwear-luxury-jacket-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737795781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792a93d10c98eace913b873%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-goose-status-symbol-outerwear-luxury-jacket-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canada%20Goose%2C%20famous%20for%20its%20luxury%20parkas%2C%20is%20a%20celebrity%20favorite.%20Here's%20how%20it%20went%20from%20making%20Antarctic%20outerwear%20and%20where%20it%20goes%20from%20here.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-goose-status-symbol-outerwear-luxury-jacket-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20make%20money%20from%20a%20TikTok%20hit.%20(Hint%3A%20You%20won't%20get%20it%20from%20TikTok.)%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Comedian%20Rachel%20Coster%20stars%20in%20Boy%20Room%2C%20a%20TikTok%20hit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f0bfeb4be2fff9a217d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBoy%20Room%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20hit%20TikTok%20show%20that%20features%20comedian%20Rachel%20Coster%20visiting%20miserable%20places%20where%20young%20men%20live.%20Amazon%20is%20sponsoring%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20show%2C%20which%20is%20owned%20by%20Gymnasium%2C%20a%20TikTok-centric%20digital%20media%20studio.%3Cp%3ELeeban%20Farah%2FGymnasium%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETikTok!%20It's%20still%20here%20in%20the%20US.%20That's%20good%20news%20for%20creators%20that%20make%20money%20working%20on%20the%20platform.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExcept%3A%20Most%20successful%20creators%20see%20very%20little%20money%20from%20TikTok%20itself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGymnasium%20cofounder%20Adam%20Faze%20explains%20how%20to%20turn%20TikTok%20eyeballs%20into%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20ago%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-trump-law-apple-google-oracle-app-store-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20disappeared%20in%20America.%20Then%20it%20was%20back%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20looks%20like%20it%20will%20stay%20that%20way%2C%20for%20at%20least%20a%20month%20or%20two%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20the%20legal%20questions%20around%20its%20existence%20remain%20%E2%80%A6%20fuzzy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20good%20news%20for%20Adam%20Faze%2C%20who%20makes%20his%20living%20on%20TikTok.%20Faze%20co-founded%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40itsgymnasium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGymnasium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20content%20studio%20that%20specializes%20in%20TikTok%20videos%2C%20with%20some%20success%3A%20Perhaps%20you've%20seen%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40boyroomshow%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoy%20Room%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20can-you-believe-this-filth%20tour%20of%20young%20men's%20...%20terrible%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Room%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20viral%20hit%20for%20Faze.%20But%20Faze%20says%20his%20company%20made%20almost%20zero%20dollars%20from%20its%20popularity.%20(Then%20again%2C%20it%20didn't%20spend%20much%2C%20either%3A%20Faze%20says%20each%20episode%20involved%20a%20crew%20of%20three%20people%20and%20cost%20around%20%242%2C000%20for%20a%20two-minute%20show.)%20The%20money%20is%20coming%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BBoy%20Room%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20sponsoring%2C%20and%20which%20will%20feature%20hints%20on%20ways%20to%20fix%20your%20Boy%20Room%20%E2%80%94%20which%20will%20involve%20buying%20things%20from%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20Faze%20this%20week%20because%20there's%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20discussion%20about%20how%20important%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-ban-influencers-are-tired-angry-cautiously-hopeful-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20is%20to%20creators%20and%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20make%20money%20on%20TikTok.%20But%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20discussion%20about%20how%20that%20actually%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TLDR%3A%20Being%20popular%20on%20TikTok%20doesn't%20translate%20to%20making%20money%20on%20TikTok%2C%20since%20TikTok%20doesn't%20routinely%20share%20its%20advertising%20money%20with%20its%20creators%20(the%20only%20TikTok%20competitor%20that%20actually%20does%20this%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E).%20The%20way%20to%20make%20money%20on%20TikTok%20is%20to%20make%20something%20popular%20that%20brands%20will%20want%20to%20be%20associated%20with%2C%20and%20work%20out%20deals%20with%20them%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20an%20edited%20excerpt%20of%20my%20conversation%20with%20Faze.%20You%20can%20hear%20the%20whole%20thing%20on%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fchannels-with-peter-kafka%2Fid1080467174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChannels%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBusiness%20Insider%3A%20Why%20start%20a%20business%20focused%20on%20TikTok%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20any%20other%20video%20platform%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Faze%3A%20It's%20the%20quickness%20of%20how%20we're%20able%20to%20see%20if%20we%20have%20a%20hit%20or%20not.%20On%20TikTok%2C%20we%20usually%20know%20within%20the%20first%20three%20episodes%20we%20post%20if%20we%20have%20a%20successful%20show.%20That%20algorithm%20is%20just%20so%20phenomenal%20at%20defining%20who%20would%20or%20would%20not%20like%20something%20that%2C%20for%20us%2C%20it%20just%20is%20a%20no-brainer%20to%20test%20shows%20%5Bon%20TikTok%5D%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20make%20money%20from%20a%20viral%20hit%20on%20TikTok%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20benefit%20of%20coming%20into%20the%20space%20years%20after%20TikTok%20was%20introduced%20is%20we%20never%20revolved%20our%20business%20model%20around%20%26quot%3BHow%20much%20is%20TikTok%20going%20to%20pay%20us%3F%26quot%3B%20We%20went%20into%20this%20company%20thinking%20we%20would%20never%20make%20a%20dollar%20from%20any%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20probably%20generated%20about%20a%20half%20a%20billion%20views%20on%20TikTok%20since%20the%20company%20started.%20I%20think%20we've%20maybe%20made%20less%20than%20%2420%2C000%20from%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouTube%20remains%20the%20only%20big%20video%20platform%20that%20consistently%20shares%20ad%20revenue%20with%20creators.%20Instagram%2C%20Snapchat%2C%20TikTok%20do%20not.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%2C%20short-form%20content%20is%20a%20great%20ad%20business%20for%20the%20platform.%20It's%20not%20for%20the%20creator%20%E2%80%94%20except%20for%20things%20now%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-tiktok-shop-is-changing-e-commerce%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETikTok%20Shop%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20you%20have%20individual%20creators%20who%20are%20making%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20a%20month%20off%20of%2C%20basically%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1bce1f2737a676f4ba1fddc9b64863d9258c58d9b29650b47372045a8d924334%26postID%3D6793ef67e2829faf19f94abd%26postSlug%3Dtiktok-money-explained-boy-room-adam-faze-peter-kafka-podcast-2025-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252