t%20shows%20%E2%80%94%20do%20we%20think%20we%20would%20be%20able%20to%20make%20money%20on%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20not%20just%20%26quot%3BWill%20people%20watch%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20but%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20something%20an%20Amazon%20or%20someone%20else%20would%20sponsor%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20give%20you%20an%20example.%20We%20used%20to%20make%20a%20show%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40clockworkdynasty%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClockwork%20Dynasty%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20with%20these%20two%20watch%20dealers%20from%2047th%20Street%20who%20are%20dear%20friends%20to%20this%20day.%20It%20was%20basically%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.com%2Fshows%2Fpawn-stars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPawn%20Stars%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20We%20built%20their%20watch%20shop%20in%20our%20office.%20People%20would%20come%20on%20the%20show%20and%20buy%2C%20sell%2C%20trade%2C%20luxury%20watches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20show%20had%20a%20consistent%201%20million-plus%20viewers%20an%20episode.%20But%20our%20audience%20was%2099%25%20boys%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2018%20and%2024%2C%20which%20in%20the%20watch%20space%20isn't%20that%20monetized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThey're%20not%20buying%20luxury%20watches.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20a%20show%20like%20that%2C%20sometimes%20you%20have%20to%20do%20the%20math.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20didn't%20make%20sense%20for%20us%20to%20keep%20making%20the%20show%2C%20even%20though%20we%20love%20it%20and%20people%20love%20it%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-money-explained-boy-room-adam-faze-peter-kafka-podcast-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737795721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f12c4bf52b7bab8a6476%3Fformat%3Djpeg