g%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScB-4a6dV6jak2g6t-CoOdxFIENDSZggxHVbvsz6ry4dGoUjg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fconstructioncoverage.com%2Fresearch%2Fwhere-residents-have-paid-off-homes%23results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOver%2060%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20homeowners%20aged%2065%20and%20older%20have%20fully%20paid%20off%20their%20mortgages%2C%20per%20an%20analysis%20of%202024%20Census%20data%20by%20the%20trade%20publication%20Construction%20Coverage.%20A%20report%20published%20in%202023%20by%20the%20retirement%20firm%20Vanguard%20also%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.vanguard.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fcorp%2Fresearch%2Fpdf%2Fhome_is_where_retirement_funding_is.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E80%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Americans%20age%2060%20and%20over%20are%20homeowners%2C%20and%20housing%20wealth%20accounts%20for%2048%25%20of%20the%20age%20group's%20median%20net%20worth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-homeowners-at-risk-of-homelessness-retirement-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan't%20afford%20to%20downsize%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20retirement%20or%20rental%20housing%20and%20struggle%20with%20the%20rising%20costs%20of%20utilities%20and%20insurance%2C%20even%20with%20the%20house%20paid-off.%20For%20these%20people%2C%20climate%20events%20are%20derailing%20meticulously%20made%20retirement%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22602a6839-6f69-488f-99f5-ab1e5250ccca%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisasters%20are%20a%20rising%20risk%20for%20older%20homeowners%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20fire%20seven%20years%20ago%2C%20Sims%2C%2081%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20moved%20four%20times%20because%20of%20rising%20housing%20costs.%20She%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20couple%20had%20worked%20hard%20to%20save%20for%20retirement%20throughout%20their%20careers%2C%20but%20most%20of%20that%20money%20was%20invested%20in%20the%20house%20they%20lost%20in%20the%20fire.%20Despite%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20they%20received%20in%20insurance%20and%20settlement%20money%2C%20it%20didn't%20come%20near%20to%20covering%20the%20full%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20limited%20savings%20left%2C%20Sims%20recently%20moved%20in%20with%20one%20of%20her%20children%20so%20that%20she%20could%20reduce%20her%20housing%20costs%20to%20cover%20the%20steep%20price%20of%20the%20memory%20care%20her%20husband%20now%20needs.%20She%20said%20what%20she%20receives%20monthly%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-social-security-works-medicare-food-stamps-retirement-elder-poverty-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%20barely%20covers%20her%20daily%20essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20nothing%20I%20could%20do%20but%20just%20watch%20the%20money%20flow%20out%20of%20my%20account%20that%20I%20had%20saved%2C%26quot%3B%20Sims%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catastrophic%20financial%20impact%20of%20disasters%20isn't%20a%20new%20problem%20for%20Americans%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20growing%20one.%20Since%201980%2C%20more%20than%20400%20weather%20and%20climate%20events%20in%20the%20US%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncei.noaa.gov%2Faccess%2Fbillions%2Fevents%2FUS%2F1980-2024%3Fdisasters%5B%5D%3Dall-disasters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexceeded%20%241%20billion%20in%20damages%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20per%20the%20National%20Centers%20for%20Environmental%20Information.%20Many%20of%20those%20storms%2C%20wildfires%2C%20and%20extreme%20temperature%20waves%20occurred%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heightened%20risk%20has%20driven%20some%20home%20insurance%20companies%20to%20raise%20premiums%2C%20restrict%20coverage%2C%20or%20cut%20plans%20altogether.%20Several%20parts%20of%20California%20and%20Florida%20have%20been%20deemed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-la-fire-damage-cost-estimate-who-pays-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euninsurable%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20And%2C%20even%20for%20those%20with%20insurance%2C%20the%20payouts%20can%20be%20slow%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fire-insurance-coverage-cancellation-no-payout-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epale%20in%20comparison%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20lost%20half%20the%20value%20of%20our%20house%20or%20more%20because%20we%20didn't%20have%20enough%20insurance.%20Every%20two%20years%2C%20we%20went%20in%20and%20upped%20the%20insurance%2C%26quot%3B%20Sims%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20she%20tried%20to%20increase%20the%20total%20amount%20of%20disaster%20coverage%20on%20the%20house%20several%20times%20before%20the%20wildfire.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20all%20the%20insurance%20companies%20would%20allow%20in%20one%20of%20those%20areas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20older%20Americans%2C%20losing%20their%20home%20can%20also%20mean%20losing%20their%20biggest%20asset%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20with%20houses%20in%20high-demand%20markets.%20A%20fifth%20of%20Americans%2050%20and%20older%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-baby-boomers-savings-cant-afford-retirement-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20retirement%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22665ccd25-7fd1-4dfe-b9e2-4b50bcbc960b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20savings%20swept%20away%20by%20disasters%2C%20older%20adults%20struggle%20to%20start%20over%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20building%20up%20a%20successful%20wholesale%20bakery%20business%2C%20Joe%20Steelhammer%20didn't%20expect%20to%20be%20living%20in%20his%20car.%20The%2073-year-old%20lives%20in%20a%20suburb%20of%20Houston%20on%20his%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESocial%20Security%20income%2C%20which%20he%20said%20isn't%20enough%20to%20pay%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteelhammer%20told%20BI%20his%20financial%20challenges%20began%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhurricane-harvey-2017-rainfall-map-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2017's%20Hurricane%20Harvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20swept%20through%20the%20area%2C%20flooding%20the%20property%20where%20he%20owned%20a%20house%20and%20a%20commercial%20kitchen.%20He%20had%20been%20working%20full-time%20baking%20cakes%2C%20quiches%2C%20and%20desserts%20for%20restaurants%20and%20hotels.%20His%20vegan%20chocolate%20truffle%20cake%20was%20especially%20popular%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20floodwaters%20receded%2C%20Steelhammer's%20home%20and%20kitchen%20were%20entirely%20destroyed.%20He%20said%20insurance%20provided%20some%20relief%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20nearly%20enough%20to%20cover%20his%20losses.%20He%20struggled%20to%20continue%20paying%20off%20the%20loans%20he%20took%20out%20to%20start%20his%20business%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Steelhammer%20said%20he%20had%20carefully%20planned%20for%20his%20retirement%20years%2C%20the%20loss%20of%20his%20home%20and%20business%20completely%20drained%20his%20savings%2C%20and%20the%20COVID%20lockdowns%20prevented%20him%20from%20regaining%20a%20reliable%20income%20through%20baking.%20He%20said%20he%20recently%20tried%20to%20apply%20for%20low-income%20housing%2C%20with%20no%20luck%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20decision%20to%20make%3A%20I%20could%20either%20afford%20rent%20or%20I%20could%20eat%20and%20pay%20my%20bills%2C%26quot%3B%20Steelhammer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20chose%20the%20latter%20of%20the%20two%2C%20and%20I%20started%20living%20in%20my%20vehicle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20older%20adults%20facing%20retirement%20losses%20from%20a%20natural%20disaster%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20impossible%20to%20start%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Shaw%2C%20director%20of%20the%20benefits%20transformation%20initiative%20at%20the%20Aspen%20Institute%2C%20suggested%20that%20people%20expand%20their%20savings%20portfolio%2C%20instead%20of%20putting%20all%20their%20money%20into%20a%20major%20asset%2C%20like%20a%20house.%20Even%20saving%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20an%20emergency%20account%20can%20help%20protect%20retirement%20savings%20and%20financial%20health%20if%20something%20unexpected%20happens%2C%20Shaw%20said%2C%20but%20he%20acknowledged%20that%20no%20one%20can%20fully%20prepare%20for%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20big%20question%20now%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20live%20in%20an%20area%20with%20a%20high%20risk%20for%20these%20sorts%20of%20disasters%2C%20whether%20putting%20all%20of%20your%20money%20and%20assets%20for%20retirement%20into%20a%20home%20is%20the%20right%20choice%2C%20or%20whether%20there's%20usefulness%20in%20diversifying%20and%20putting%20some%20of%20that%20money%20into%20retirement%20savings%20instead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20natural%20disasters%20can%20impact%20people%20at%20any%20age%20or%20stage%20in%20their%20financial%20journey.%20Sims%20wishes%20more%20people%20understood%20the%20way%20a%20disaster%20can%20impact%20every%20facet%20of%20life%2C%20even%20those%20who%20feel%20prepared%20for%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20budgeted%20and%20followed%20that%20budget%2C%20we%20knew%20exactly%20how%20much%20money%20we%20needed%2C%20and%20we%20planned%20on%20our%20needs%20for%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Sims%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20we%20didn't%20plan%20for%20a%20wildfire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20you%20experienced%20financial%20challenges%20due%20to%20a%20natural%20disaster%3F%20Are%20you%20open%20to%20sharing%20your%20experience%20with%20a%20reporter%3F%20If%20so%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aallisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eallisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-disasters-impact-older-homeowners-retirement-savings-insurance-la-wildfires-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737795601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67929c1610c98eace913b5a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-disasters-impact-older-homeowners-retirement-savings-insurance-la-wildfires-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20natural%20disasters%20become%20more%20severe%2C%20older%20Americans'%20homes%20are%20at%20risk.%20But%2C%20for%20many%2C%20their%20house%20is%20their%20biggest%20retirement%20asset.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22allisonkelly%40businessinsider.com%20(Allie%20Kelly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-disasters-impact-older-homeowners-retirement-savings-insurance-la-wildfires-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ranji%20Trophy%20LIVE%3A%20Mumbai%20Staring%20At%20Defeat%20On%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Ranji%20Return%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%20vs%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20LIVE%20Updates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20Ranji%20Trophy%20comeback%20is%20staring%20at%20defeat%2C%20but%20has%20received%20some%20hope%20as%20Mumbai%20made%20some%20much-needed%20breakthroughs%20against%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20Having%20been%20set%20a%20target%20of%20205%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20were%20112%2F1%2C%20but%20then%20fell%20to%20159%2F5%2C%20giving%20some%20hope%20of%20a%20lat