come%20up%2012%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737792024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Flive-news-updates-india-narendra-modi-temperature-aqi-mahakumbh-trump-jaishankar-delhi-polls-125012500089_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Latest%20news%20updates%3A%20Catch%20all%20the%20major%20news%20updates%20from%20around%20the%20world%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Polio%20Returns%20To%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20As%20Vaccinations%20Stall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoliomyelitis%20was%20responsible%20for%20paralysing%20and%20killing%20up%20to%20half%20a%20million%20people%20every%20year%20before%20the%20development%20of%20the%20poliovirus%20vaccine%20in%201955.%20By%202000%2C%20through%20mass%20vaccination%20campaigns%20of%20oral%20polio%20vaccines%2C%20the%20world%20had%20almost%20eradicated%20poiliovirus%20barring%20a%20few%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20global%20fight%20against%20polio%20has%20encountered%20a%20significant%20setback%2C%20as%20cases%20of%20the%20disease%20have%20begun%20to%20rise%20again%20in%20Pakistan.%20Despite%20being%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20eradication%20in%202023%2C%20with%20only%20six%20reported%20cases%20of%20the%20wild%20form%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20the%20number%20of%20cases%20has%20surged%20to%2073%20in%202024.%20This%20alarming%20trend%20has%20prompted%20concerns%20among%20health%20experts%2C%20who%20point%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Afghanistan%20as%20a%20major%20factor%20contributing%20to%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20data%20from%20the%20WHO%2C%20infectious%20diseases%20such%20as%20pneumonia%2C%20dengue%20fever%20and%20measles%20have%20also%20been%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20Afghanistan%20since%20the%20last%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZulfiqar%20Bhutta%2C%20a%20renowned%20expert%20on%20child%20immunisation%20strategies%20in%20conflict%20zones%2C%20said%20that%20the%20genetic%20strains%20of%20wild%20poliovirus%20in%20Pakistan%20are%20all%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20per%20a%20report%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fas-vaccination-falters-polio-back-in-afghanistan-pakistan%2Fa-71400634%5C%22%3EDeutsche%20Welle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutta%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20extensively%20in%20the%20region%2C%20attributes%20the%20resurgence%20of%20polio%20cases%20in%20Pakistan%20to%20the%20spillover%20of%20the%20virus%20from%20Afghanistan.%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20spread%20to%20all%20districts%20of%20Pakistan.%20We've%20snatched%20defeat%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhutta%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20virus%20that%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20eradicated%2C%20so%20give%20it%20an%20inch%20and%20it%20will%20take%20a%20yard%2C%26quot%3B%20Bhutta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20facing%20polio%20eradication%20efforts%20in%20the%20region%20are%20multifaceted.%20Bhutta%20cites%20the%20Taliban's%20restrictions%20on%20female%20health%20professionals%2C%20poor%20sanitary%20conditions%2C%20and%20regional%20insecurity%20as%20significant%20obstacles.%20The%20lack%20of%20reliable%20data%20on%20poliovirus%20cases%20in%20Afghanistan%20further%20complicates%20efforts%20to%20combat%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20invested%20heavily%20in%20poliovirus%20immunisation%20programs%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20%2410%20billion%20spent%20since%202011.%20Despite%20these%20efforts%2C%20the%20country's%20progress%20in%20eradicating%20the%20disease%20has%20been%20uneven%2C%20with%20varying%20immunisation%20rates%20across%20provinces.%20In%20Punjab%2C%2085%25%20of%20children%20are%20vaccinated%2C%20while%20in%20Balochistan%20the%20rate%20is%20as%20low%20as%2030%25.%20Until%20the%20coverage%20reaches%2085-90%25%20in%20all%20provinces%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20to%20eradicate%20it%2C%20Bhutta%20said.%20He%20also%20emphasises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20immunisation%20strategies%2C%20highlighting%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20routine%20immunisation%20programs%20for%20all%20infectious%20diseases%2C%20not%20just%20polio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhutta's%20expertise%20in%20working%20with%20the%20Taliban%20in%20Afghanistan%20offers%20valuable%20insights%20into%20the%20complexities%20of%20delivering%20healthcare%20services%20in%20conflict%20zones.%20He%20stresses%20that%20the%20Taliban%20are%20not%20the%20enemy%20and%20that%20they%20share%20the%20same%20health%20concerns%20as%20everyone%20else.%20Bhutta's%20experience%20in%20working%20with%20the%20Taliban%20to%20deliver%20smallpox%20vaccines%20during%20periods%20of%20negotiated%20peace%20underscores%20the%20potential%20for%20collaboration%20in%20addressing%20health%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20resurgence%20of%20polio%20cases%20in%20Pakistan%20serves%20as%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20for%20sustained%20efforts%20in%20combating%20infectious%20diseases.%20Bhutta's%20call%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20immunisation%20strategies%20and%20his%20emphasis%20on%20addressing%20broader%20health%20needs%20in%20the%20region%20offer%20a%20way%20forward%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20polio.%20Ultimately%2C%20eradicating%20poliovirus%20in%20the%20region%20will%20require%20a%20concerted%20effort%20from%20international%20and%20local%20health%20authorities%2C%20as%20well%20as%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Taliban%20government%20in%20Afghanistan.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737791640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2F6g2u64t8_pakistan-polio-generic-afp_625x300_25_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpolio-returns-to-pakistan-afghanistan-as-vaccinations-stall-75