0Personnel%20Office%2C%20focusing%20on%20staffing%20and%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20journalist%20Kush%20Desai%20steps%20in%20as%20Deputy%20Press%20Secretary%20for%20a%20role%20in%20the%20White%20House's%20communications%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20a%20closer%20look%20at%20these%20appointees%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ERicky%20Gill%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERicky%20Gill%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20international%20relations%2C%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20(NSC)%2C%20where%20he%20previously%20served%20as%20Director%20for%20Russia%20and%20European%20Energy%20Security%20during%20Trump's%20first%20term.%20In%20addition%20to%20his%20work%20at%20the%20NSC%2C%20he%20served%20as%20a%20Senior%20Advisor%20in%20the%20State%20Department's%20Bureau%20of%20Overseas%20Buildings%20Operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20the%20administration%2C%20Mr%20Gill%20led%20Gill%20Capital%20Group%20as%20Principal%20and%20General%20Counsel%20and%20acted%20as%20an%20adviser%20on%20European%20and%20Asian%20energy%20for%20TC%20Energy%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20Keystone%20XL%20Pipeline.%20This%20project%2C%20partially%20greenlit%20by%20Trump%2C%20was%20halted%20by%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Lodi%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20Mr%20Gill%20holds%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20from%20Princeton%20University's%20Woodrow%20Wilson%20School%20of%20Public%20and%20International%20Affairs%20and%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaurabh%20Sharma%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBengaluru-born%20Saurabh%20Sharma%20most%20recently%20served%20as%20the%20President%20of%20American%20Moment%2C%20a%20conservative%20organisation%20focused%20on%20personnel%20development%2C%20according%20to%20Politico.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20graduated%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20Biochemistry%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Texa