Trump's%20favored%20television%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHegseth%20has%20a%20combative%20media%20personality%2C%20fierce%20loyalty%20and%20telegenic%20looks%20--%20common%20hallmarks%20in%20Trump's%20entourage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20say%20Hegseth's%20deployments%20in%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iraq%20give%20him%20the%20insight%20to%20run%20the%20Defense%20Department%20better%20than%20more%20experienced%20officials%20who%20would%20normally%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20pledged%20to%20focus%20the%20military%20on%20%26quot%3Blethality%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20bring%20back%20%26quot%3Bwarrior%20culture%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20confirming%20him%2C%20Republicans%20brushed%20aside%20his%20lack%20of%20experience%20leading%20an%20organization%20anywhere%20near%20the%20size%20of%20the%20Defense%20Department%20--%20the%20country's%20largest%20employer%20with%20some%20three%20million%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20approved%20Hegseth%20despite%20allegations%20of%20financial%20mismanagement%20at%20veterans'%20nonprofits%20where%20he%20previously%20worked%2C%20reports%20of%20excessive%20drinking%2C%20and%20allegations%20that%20he%20sexually%20assaulted%20a%20woman%20in%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20during%20his%20confirmation%20hearing%20last%20week%20about%20criticism%20he%20has%20faced%2C%20Hegseth%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoordinated%20smear%20campaign%26quot%3B%20against%20him%2C%20and%20that%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20perfect%20person%2C%20but%20redemption%20is%20real.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20stood%20by%20him%2C%20telling%20reporters%20Friday%3A%20%26quot%3BPete's%20a%20very%2C%20very%20good%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Erratic%20and%20aggressive%20behavior'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20three%20Republicans%20--%20senators%20Susan%20Collins%2C%20Mitch%20McConnell%20and%20Lisa%20Murkowski%20--%20were%20unconvinced%20and%20voted%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMurkowski%20said%20on%20X%20the%20day%20before%20the%20Friday%20vote%20that%20%26quot%3Bpast%20behaviors%20Mr%20Hegseth%20has%20admitted%20to%2C%20including%20infidelity%20on%20multiple%20occasions%2C%20demonstrate%20a%20lack%20of%20judgment%20that%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20someone%20who%20would%20lead%20our%20armed%20forces.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20his%20approval%20by%20the%20full%20Senate%2C%20lawmakers%20received%20an%20affidavit%20from%20Hegseth's%20former%20sister-in-law%20Danielle%20Hegseth%20that%20added%20to%20the%20allegations%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20Hegseth%20has%20an%20alcohol%20abuse%20problem%20and%20was%20abusive%20to%20his%20ex-wife%20Samantha%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20affidavit%20said%2C%20though%20it%20noted%20that%20Danielle%20Hegseth%20did%20not%20personally%20witness%20physical%20or%20sexual%20abuse%20by%20the%20incoming%20defense%20secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDanielle%20Hegseth%20however%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20observed...%20Hegseth's%20erratic%20and%20aggressive%20behavior%20over%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20she%20was%20subjected%20to%20emotional%20abuse%20by%20him%2C%20and%20that%20she%20was%20told%20by%20his%20ex-wife%20that%20she%20once%20hid%20from%20him%20in%20a%20closet%20because%20she%20%26quot%3Bfeared%20for%20her%20personal%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20affidavit%2C%20Hegseth%20also%20told%20his%20ex-sister-in-law%20that%20women%20should%20not%20work%20or%20have%20the%20right%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BChristians%20needed%20to%20have%20more%20children%20so%20they%20can%20overtake%20the%20Muslim%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20combative%20confirmation%20hearing%2C%20Hegseth%20stuck%20to%20his%20opposition%20to%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20policies%20--%20long%20a%20bugbear%20for%20Republicans%20--%20saying%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdividing%20troops%20inside%20formations%2C%20causing%20commanders%20to%20walk%20on%20eggshells%2C%20not%20putting%20meritocracy%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20sought%20to%20soften%20past%20remarks%20opposing%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%2C%20telling%20lawmakers%20that%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20will%20have%20access%20to%20ground%20combat%20roles...%20given%20the%20standards%20remain%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20more%20of%20Trump's%20most%20contentious%20nominees%20will%20soon%20be%20grilled%20by%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKash%20Patel%20--%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20lead%20the%20FBI%20--%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20his%20pick%20for%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%2C%20and%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20the%20president's%20choice%20for%20secretary%20of%20health%20and%20human%20services%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20Senate%20hearings%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737776760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8diivb0o_pete-hegseth_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrumps-controversial-pick-pete-hegseth-confirmed-as-us-defence-secretary-7554110%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Senate%20narrowly%20confirmed%20former%20Fox%20News%20co-host%20Pete%20Hegseth%20as%20Pentagon%20chief%20on%20Friday%2C%20despite%20allegations%20of%20alcohol%20abuse%2C%20sexual%20misconduct%20and%20other%20fears%20about%20his%20ability%20to%20lead%20the%20world's%20most%20powerful%20military.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Box%20Office%3A%20Sky%20Force%20Marks%20Akshay's%20Big%20Comeback%20With%20Double-Di