ualifications%20for%20the%20position%20have%20all%20been%20under%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Fox%20News%20host's%20confirmation%20hearing%20in%20January%2C%20he%20faced%20intense%20questioning%2C%20walking%20back%20previous%20comments%20he%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-pentagon-pick-walked-back-his-outspoken-opposition-to-women-in-combat-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagainst%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20promising%20to%20bring%20a%20warrior%20ethos%20back%20to%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20received%20support%20from%20many%20Republicans%20and%20veterans.%20Tim%20Kennedy%2C%20a%20retired%20Army%20Green%20Beret%20and%20mixed%20martial%20artist%2C%20has%20repeatedly%20advocated%20for%20Hegseth's%20candidacy%2C%20calling%20him%20%26quot%3Ban%20agent%20of%20change.%26quot%3B%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20John%20Thune%2C%20a%20South%20Dakota%20Republican%2C%20said%20that%20Hegseth%20would%20bring%20%26quot%3Ba%20warrior's%20perspective%20to%20the%20role%20of%20defense%20secretary%20and%20will%20provide%20much-needed%20fresh%20air%20at%20the%20Pentagon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth's%20confirmation%20may%20bring%20radical%20changes%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20that%20had%20been%20resisted%20in%20Trump's%20first%20term.%20It%20was%20Hegseth%20who%20then%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpete-hegseth-advocated-pardons-of-us-troops-accused-of-war-crimes-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvised%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trump%20to%20pardon%20troops%20accused%20or%20convicted%20of%20war%20crimes%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-listened-fox-host-pete-hegesth-over-his-secretary-defense-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eobjections%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20top%20Pentagon%20leaders%20who%20worried%20this%20would%20erode%20the%20discipline%20and%20order%20in%20their%20ranks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225469%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pete%20Hegseth%20wearing%20a%20grey%20suit%20and%20camouflage%20print%20tie%20speaking%20into%20microphones%20held%20by%20reporters%20at%20Capitol%20Hill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f714196626c40984fa9b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESenators%20questioned%20Hegseth%20about%20his%20personal%20life%2C%20views%2C%20and%20experience.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20rhetoric%20and%20background%2C%20Hegseth%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20lawmakers%20and%20officials%20as%20an%20unconventional%20pick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20who%20served%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Afghanistan%2C%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20National%20Guard%20members%20who%20had%20their%20orders%20to%20secure%20then%20President-elect%20Joe%20Biden's%20inauguration%20revoked%20after%20the%20January%206%20insurrection%20due%20to%20controversy%20over%20his%20tattoo%20of%20a%20Jerusalem%20cross%3B%20he%20also%20has%20a%20tattoo%20of%20a%20Christian%20motto%20that%20dates%20to%20the%20Crusades%20and%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%20the%20alt-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%20has%20also%20received%20backlash%20over%20his%20views%20of%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%20roles.%20During%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDoN5ovwB8s4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20podcast%20episode%20after%20Trump's%20reelection%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Hegseth%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20straight-up%20just%20saying%20we%20should%20not%20have%20women%20in%20combat%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20it%20hurt%20the%20military's%20readiness.%20At%20his%20confirmation%20hearing%20in%20January%2C%20he%20took%20a%20different%20tone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYes%2C%20women%20will%20have%20access%20to%20ground%20combat%20roles%2C%20given%20the%20standards%20remain%20high%2C%20and%20we'll%20have%20a%20review%20to%20ensure%20the%20standards%20have%20not%20been%20eroded%20in%20any%20one%20of%20these%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20Hegseth%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20if%20he's%20confirmed%2C%20he'll%20initiate%20a%20review%20of%20gender-neutral%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pete%20Hegseth%20wearing%20a%20black%20tuxedo%20talking%20to%20someone%20with%20people%20standing%20around%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793f68c196626c40984fa67%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222153%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHegseth%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20bring%20warrior%20ethos%20back%20to%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20will%20order%20a%20review%20of%20physical%20standards%20for%20military%20jobs.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20been%20grilled%20about%20his%20drinking%2C%20beliefs%20against%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%2C%20and%20his%20personal%20history.%20During%20a%20media%20blitz%20to%20shore%20up%20his%20struggling%20candidacy%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress%2F-back-embattled-hegseth-says-trump-told-keep-fighting-rcna182855%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evowed%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthere%20won't%20be%20a%20drop%20of%20alcohol%20on%20my%20lips%26quot%3B%20while%20he's%20the%20SECDEF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20sexual%20assault%20allegations%20against%20Hegseth%20from%20an%20incident%20in%202017%20were%20made%20public.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Hegseth%20told%20police%20that%20the%20encounter%20was%20consensual%20and%20denied%20any%20wrongdoing%3B%20he%20was%20never%20criminally%20charged.%20In%20November%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20fully%20investigated%20and%20he'd%20been%20cleared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHegseth%2C%20an%20avowed%20opponent%20of%20the%20Defense%20Department's%20efforts%20to%20d