%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20the%20%24500%20billion%20AI%20project%2C%20Stargate%2C%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStargate's%20first%20data%20center%20is%20under%20construction%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas%2C%20said%20Oracle%20CTO%20Larry%20Ellison.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPublic%20filings%20for%20an%20Abilene%20development%20matching%20Ellison's%20description%20shed%20some%20light%20on%20costs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20on%20what%20appears%20to%20be%20two%20buildings%20on%20Stargate's%20first%20data%20center%20campus%2C%20now%20underway%20in%20Texas%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20complete%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%20and%20cost%20an%20estimated%20%241.1%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20public%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20announced%20the%20formation%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-ai-stargate-openai-oracle-softbank-technology-investment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20Oracle%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20SoftBank%2C%20at%20a%20White%20House%20press%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%20He%20pledged%20to%20spend%20%24500%20billion%20building%20AI%20data%20centers%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20founder%20and%20CTO%20Larry%20Ellison%2C%20who%20joined%20Trump%2C%20OpenAI%20CEO%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-trump-stargate-build-agi-us-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESam%20Altman%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20SoftBank%20CEO%20Masayoshi%20Son%20at%20the%20briefing%2C%20said%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproject-stargate-ai-deepseek-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%3C%2Fa%3E%20data%20centers%20are%20currently%20being%20built%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20working%20with%20OpenAI%20for%20a%20while%20and%20Masa%20for%20a%20while.%20The%20data%20centers%20are%20actually%20under%20construction%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20of%20them%20are%20under%20construction%20in%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ellison.%20%26quot%3BEach%20building%20is%20a%20half%20million%20square%20feet.%20There%20are%2010%20buildings%20currently%20being%20built%2C%20but%20that%20will%20expand%20to%2020%20and%20other%20locations%20beyond%20the%20Abilene%20location%2C%20which%20is%20our%20first%20location.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELittle%20else%20has%20been%20revealed%20about%20Stargate.%20Registration%20forms%20filed%20with%20the%20Texas%20Department%20of%20Licensing%20and%20Regulation%20for%20a%20data%20center%20development%20in%20Abilene%20matching%20Ellison's%20description%20of%20Stargate%20give%20some%20insight%20into%20the%20cost%20of%20building%20the%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20is%20registered%20with%20the%20TDLR%20under%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BProject%20Ludicrous%2C%26quot%3B%20located%20at%20an%20address%20attached%20to%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20%E2%80%94%20a%201%2C000-acre%20site%20in%20Abilene%20owned%20by%20energy%20tech%20company%20Lancium.%20The%20owner%20of%20Project%20Ludicrous%20is%20listed%20as%20Abilene%20DC%201%20LLC%2C%20an%20affiliate%20of%20data%20center%20development%20startup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-gpu-chips-demand-artificial-intelligence-debt-investing-cloud-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrusoe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20the%20Texas%20state%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcomptroller.texas.gov%2Ftaxes%2Fdata-centers%2Fdata-center-lists.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomptroller's%20records%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Oracle%20is%20the%20occupant%20of%20the%20data%20center%20owned%20by%20Abilene%20DC%201%2C%20LLC%2C%20located%20at%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20in%20Abilene.%20A%20Texas-based%20Oracle%20employee%20is%20also%20listed%20as%20the%20tenant%20contact%20for%20Project%20Ludicrous%20in%20the%20TDLR%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20July%20and%20December%202024%2C%20agents%20for%20Project%20Ludicrous%20filed%20four%20different%20TDLR%20filings%20for%20two%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConstruction%20on%20the%20first%20building%2C%20a%20482%2C000-square-foot%20one-story%20%26quot%3Bdata%20hall%26quot%3B%20estimated%20to%20cost%20%24292%20million%2C%20began%20in%20June%202024%20and%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20May%2030%2C%202025.%20The%20estimate%20also%20includes%20plans%20for%20a%20guard%20house%2C%20fire%20pump%20building%2C%20and%20mechanical%20and%20electrical%20enclosures.%20A%20second%20filing%20for%20the%20building%2C%20made%20in%20September%2C%20indicates%20that%20tenant%20improvements%20costing%20%24140%20million%20began%20in%20December%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20by%20September%2015%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20second%20building%20registered%20under%20Project%20Ludicrous%2C%20a%20484%2C960-square-foot%20%26quot%3B1-story%20data%20center%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20cost%20estimate%20of%20%24292%20million%2C%20went%20under%20construction%20in%20September%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20one%20year%2C%20the%20filings%20said.%20Tenant%20improvements%2C%20expected%20to%20begin%20in%20March%20and%20be%20completed%20by%20December%2024%2C%20are%20estimated%20at%20%24384%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20San%20Antonio%20Express-News%20previously%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.expressnews.com%2Fbusiness%2Farticle%2Ftrump-ai-partnership-texas-projects-20047850.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20these%20filings%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELancium%2C%20the%20landowner%2C%20first%20struck%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopabilene.com%2F2024%2F11%2F19%2Fthe-development-corporation-of-abilene-city-of-abilene-and-taylor-county-announce-expanded-development-within-lanciums-clean-campus-through-crusoes-998000-square-foot-data-center%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edevelopment%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20city%20of%20Abilene%20in%202021%20for%20what%20it%20calls%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus.%20The%20site%20was%20initially%20meant%20to%20power%20bitcoin%20mines%20with%20renewable%20energy%20generation%2C%20although%20that%20never%20came%20to%20fruition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20Crusoe%20announced%20plans%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrusoe.ai%2Fnewsroom%2Fcrusoe-blue-owl-capital-primary-digital-joint-venture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%243.4%20billion%20data%20center%20development%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20and%20said%20it%20had%20already%20fully%20leased%20the%20space%20to%20a%20%26quot%3BFortune%20100%20hyperscale%20tenant%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20occupancy%20expected%20to%20begin%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Information%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D08f73f3dcd6c3cba0d9ca805dde0e97571b2817b7be04db63533e67dc3dcc8f7%26postID%3D6793a64922e74339bb4d0eec%26postSlug%3Dtexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theinformation.com%252Farticles%252Fwhy-openai-and-oracles-ai-data-center-plan-hinges-on-a-little-known-startup%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20Oracle's%20plans%20to%20lease%20a%20data%20center%20site%20in%20Texas%20from%20Crusoe%2C%20intending%20to%20eventually%20rent%20servers%20to%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fannouncing-the-stargate-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20website%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20that%20the%20Stargate%20%26quot%3Bbuildout%20is%20currently%20underway%2C%20starting%20in%20Texas%2C%20and%20we%20are%20evaluating%20potential%20sites%20across%20the%20country%20for%20more%20campuses%20as%20we%20finalize%20definitive%20agreements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLancium%20is%20excited%20to%20be%20building%20its%20Lancium%20Clean%20Campus%20in%20Abilene%2C%20Texas%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Crusoe%20and%20the%20Development%20Corporation%20of%20Abilene%20(DCOA)%20and%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20growth%20of%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20industry%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Lancium%20wrote%20in%20response%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20could%20not%20%26quot%3Bprovide%20any%20new%20commentary%20about%20Abilene%20or%20any%20of%20our%20other%20Clean%20Campuses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20Crusoe%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20insight%2C%20information%2C%20or%20a%20tip%20to%20share%20with%20this%20reporter%3F%20Contact%20Ellen%20Thomas%20via%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20%2B1-929-524-6964.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737769047000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6794304c196626c4098505f6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stargate's%20first%20data%20center%20campus%20in%20Texas%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20by%20Oracle%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20SoftBank%2C%20could%20cost%20an%20estimated%20%241.1%20billion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Ellen%20Thomas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A515%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B4%20Spinners%20Not%20Viable...%26quot%3B%3A%20Big%20Doubts%20Over%20BCCI's%20CT%20India%20Squad%20Raised%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20all-rounder%20Irfan%20Pathan%20has%20backed%20India's%20move%20to%20delay%20Mohammed%20Shami's%20much-anticipated%20international%20return%20following%20a%20prolonged%20injury%20lay-off%2C%20saying%20the%20team%20think%20tank%20and%20the%20veteran%20pacer%20will%20make%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20call%20at%20the%20right%20time%26quot%3B.%20Shami%2C%20who%20has%20proved%20his%20fitness%20in%20practice%20sessions%20and%20domestic%20cricket%20for%20Bengal%2C%20was%20not%20included%20in%20India's%20playing%20XI%20for%20the%20first%20T20I%20against%20England%20here%20on%20Wednesday.%20All%20eyes%20were%20on%20Shami's%20return%20after%20a%2014-month%20injury%20lay-off%2C%20but%20India%20opted%20for%20three%20spinners%20instead%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20paid%20off%20as%20they%20bowled%20out%20England%20for%20a%20meagre%20132%20before%20cruising%20to%20the%20target%20in%2012.5%20overs%20with%20seven%20wickets%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20said%20Shami%20is%20experienced%20enough%20to%20take%20an%20honest%20assessment%20of%20his%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you've%20been%20such%20a%20seasoned%20campaigner%20and%20are%20among%20India's%20top%2010%20bowlers%2C%20you%20understand%20your%20body's%20limits%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Irfan%20at%20a%20promotional%20event%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShami%20always%20provides%20honest%20feedback%20to%20the%20team%20management%2C%20and%20decisions%20are%20made%20through%20mutual%20communication.%20Recovery%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20takes%20time%2C%20especially%20after%20playing%20consistently.%20I%20believe%20he%20and%20the%20team%20management%20will%20make%20the%20right%20call%20at%20the%20right%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20undergone%20surgery%20and%20rehab%20following%20an%20ankle%20injury%20sustained%20during%20the%202023%20ODI%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20he%20finished%20as%20India's%20top%20wicket-taker%2C%20Shami%20had%20made%20an%20impressive%20return%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20representing%20Bengal%20across%20all%20three%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%20has%20been%20chosen%20in%20India's%20white-ball%20rubber%20squad%20against%20England%20consisting%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20which%20will%20act%20as%20a%20build%20up%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20next%20month%2C%20where%20the%20team's%20pace%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah's%20inclusion%20is%20subject%20to%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%20suffered%20a%20back%20niggle%20in%20the%20gruelling%20five-match%20Test%20series%20in%20Australia%20and%20could%20not%20bowl%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20of%20the%20fifth%20Test%20in%20Sydney%2C%20and%20in%20this%20context%20Shami's%20availability%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20crucial%20to%20India's%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20expressed%20concerns%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20pace-bowling%20backup%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy-bound%20squad%2C%20suggesting%20that%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20could%20have%20been%20included%20given%20Bumrah's%20uncertain%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20a%20backup%20pacer.%20Siraj%20could%20have%20been%20a%20good%20option.%20In%20Dubai%2C%20playing%20four%20spinners%20isn't%20viable.%20With%20Bumrah%20and%20Shami%20returning%20from%20injuries%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20easy%20for%20them%20straight%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20pacer%20like%20Siraj%20would%20have%20filled%20that%20gap.%20That%20said%2C%20we%20hope%20the%20selectors'%20choices%20perform%20well%2C%20and%20we%20should%20back%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20addressed%20the%20poor%20form%20of%20senior%20batters%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20during%20India's%201-3%20series%20defeat%20in%20the%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20--%20India's%20first%20series%20loss%20in%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20advised%20fans%20not%20to%20conflate%20the%20celebrated%20duo's%20Test%20struggles%20with%20their%20prospects%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey'll%20start%20scoring%20runs%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%3B%20there's%20no%20doubt%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Irfan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTest%20cricket%20is%20a%20different%20ball%20game%20altogether.%20Adjustments%20are%20needed%2C%20whether%20it's%20Virat%20managing%20deliveries%20outside%20the%20off-stump%20or%20Rohit%20finding%20his%20rhythm.%20ODI%20is%20their%20favourite%20format%2C%20and%20they'll%20bounce%20back%20strongly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20India's%20resilience%20during%20the%202003-04%20Australia%20tour%2C%20Irfan%20further%20shared%20a%20motivational%20anecdote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBack%20then%2C%20Dean%20Jones%20visited%20our%20dressing%20room%20and%20mentioned%20how%20outsiders%20thought%20our%20team%20environment%20was%20broken.%20But%20we%20showed%20unity%20on%20the%20field%20and%20drew%20the%20series%201-1.%20Indian%20cricket%20is%20always%20above%20individual%20concerns%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIrfan%20also%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20urging%20players%20to%20participate%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20playing%20domestic%20cricket%20but%20do%20not%20play%20a%20couple%20of%20matches%20just%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20it%20and%20show%20that%20you've%20played.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlaying%20regularly%20benefits%20both%20players%20and%20Indian%20cricket.%20For%20young%20players%2C%20competing%20against%20the%20likes%20of%20Kohli%20or%20Rohit%20at%20the%20domestic%20level%20can%20be%20a%20tremendous%20confidence%20boost%20as%20they%20would%20also%20raise%20their%20levels%20to%20bowl%20to%20them.%20Ultimately%2C%20Indian%20cricket%20gains%20from%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2