0to%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20transformative%20potential%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20in%20remote%20and%20very%20complex%20regions%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20leaders%20are%20putting%20aside%20their%20personal%20grief%20and%20challenges%20while%20addressing%20historically%20overlooked%20issues%20in%20places%20like%C2%A0%20Muzzafarpur%2C%20Madhubani%2C%20Supaul%20and%20Vaishali%20in%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Mahoba%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReclaiming%20the%20dignity%20of%20widows%20in%20Bihar%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theloombafoundation.org%2Fworld-widow-report%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELoomba%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20(2022)%2C%20there%20are%20over%20245%20million%20widowed%20women%20globally%2C%20with%20India%20alone%20accounting%20for%2017%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20flood-prone%20regions%20%E2%80%94%20widows%2C%20particularly%20from%20vulnerable%20communities%20like%20the%20Musahars%2C%20a%20marginalised%20group%20enduring%20historic%20discrimination%20in%20the%20eastern%20Gangetic%20plain%2C%20face%20compounded%20vulnerabilities.%C2%A0%20Here%2C%20floods%20not%20only%20devastate%20infrastructure%20but%20also%20deny%20women%20access%20to%20stable%20livelihoods%2C%20social%20support%2C%20and%20dignity%2C%20reinforcing%20cycles%20of%20poverty%20and%20exclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20rural%20Muzaffarpur%2C%20Bandana%2C%20faced%20the%20challenge%20of%20navigating%20life%20without%20a%20partner%2C%20securing%20entitlements%20like%20widow%20pensions%2C%20while%20regaining%20financial%20independence.%20Her%20personal%20struggle%20revealed%20to%20her%20the%20harsher%20realities%20for%20widows%20from%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20who%20are%20often%20left%20voiceless%20and%20invisible.%20Whil