hood%20and%20remarriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20work%20begins%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20focusing%20on%20local%20governance%20and%20community%20engagement.%20We%20bring%20to%20notice%20the%20discrimination%20faced%20by%20women%20from%20marginalised%20groups.%20By%20building%20community%20committees%20and%20passing%20resolutions%2C%20we%20ensure%20these%20critical%20issues%20are%20prioritised%20and%20addressed%20collectively%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bandana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20Bandana%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20distinctive%20is%20her%20dedication%20to%20shared%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edecision%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fstrong%3Emaking%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhere%20widows%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%20shape%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20priorities.%20Together%2C%20they%20break%20stereotypes%2C%20build%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20demand%20rights%20long%20denied%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20her%20work%2C%20Bandana%20demonstrates%20how%20women%2C%20even%20in%20the%20most%20challenging%20circumstances%2C%20can%20be%20agents%20of%20change%2C%20turning%20marginalisation%20into%20empowerment%20and%20reclaiming%20dignity%20for%20themselves%20and%20their%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20Bundelkhand%2C%20liberation%20can%20take%20different%20shapes%20and%20forms%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20conservative%20joint%20family%20in%20Bundelkhand%2C%20Kalpana%2C%20the%20eldest%20of%20five%20daughters%2C%20often%20felt%20the%20weight%20of%20societal%20expectations.%20Though%20she%20had%20access%20to%20education%2C%20the%20pressure%20to%20conform%20to%20rigid%20gender%20norms%20was%20ever-present.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20early%20marriage%20to%20a%20doctor%2C%20Kalpana%20found%20herself%20in%20what%20initially%20seemed%20like%20another%20extension%20of%20patriarchal%20control.%20However%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20the%20first%20time%20she%20ex