ch%20as%20jaggery%20and%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20and%20iron%20tablets.%20My%20haemoglobin%20was%2010%20%5Bnormal%20range%20is%2012.0-15.5%20g%2FdL%5D.%20I%20followed%20all%20the%20instructions%20and%20my%20baby%20was%20born%20a%20month%20back.%20Both%20of%20us%20are%20healthy%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20provide%20much-needed%20diagnostic%20services%20to%20underserved%20populations%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20Parida%20IAS%20spearheaded%20the%20Nirikhyana%20initiative%20in%20Ganjam%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConceptualised%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20programme%20aims%20to%20address%20the%20glaring%20gap%20in%20access%20to%20essential%20diagnostic%20services%2C%20especially%20ultrasounds%20for%20pregnant%20women%2C%20in%20remote%20villages.%20Formally%20launched%20in%202023%2C%20this%20service%20has%20significantly%20improved%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F45181%2Ftribal-women-india-odisha-maternal-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20and%20child%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20providing%20reassurance%20to%201.38%20lakh%20pregnant%20women%2C%20including%20Jhili%2C%20during%20a%20vulnerable%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBridging%20the%20diagnostic%20gap%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20extensive%20field%20visits%20and%20review%20meetings%20after%20his%20joining%20in%20July%202022%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20found%20a%20critical%20lack%20of%20ultrasound%20facilities%20in%20rural%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20gap%20left%20many%20pregnant%20women%20without%20access%20to%20the%20necessary%20ultrasounds%20during%20their%20nine-month%20gestation%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20District%20Collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20diagnostic%20services%20were%20concentrated%20mostly%20in%20urban%20areas%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20remotely%20placed%20villages%20to%20access%20these%20services.%20This%20motivated%20us%20to%20bridge%20the%20gap%20and%20use%20technology%20for%20a%20real-time%20assessment%20of%20diagnostic%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ganjam%20district%20administration%20launched%20the%20Nirikhyana%20scheme%20to%20offer%20free%20USG%20services%20to%20pregnant%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-1-1737031907-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Ganjam%20district%20administration%20launched%20the%20Nirikhyana%20scheme%20to%20offer%20free%20USG%20services%20to%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20first%20gap%20%E2%80%94%20availability%20of%20services%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Nirikhyana%20scheme%20invited%20private%20players%20to%20collaborate%20with%20government%20services.%20This%20Public%20Private%20Partnership%20(PPP)%20approach%20ensures%20that%20both%20government%20and%20private%20diagnostic%20centres%20provide%20services%2C%20expanding%20reach%20exponentially.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20women%2C%20who%20had%20to%20travel%20up%20to%2075%20kilometres%20for%20an%20ultrasound%2C%20can%20now%20access%20facilities%20within%20their%20blocks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20the%20partnership%2C%20about%2042%20government%20and%20private%20clinics%20are%20offering%20up%20to%20three%20free%20ultrasound%20scans%20to%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20gap%2C%20Dibyajyoti%20points%20out%2C%20was%20data%20transmission.%20To%20ensure%20seamless%20communication%20among%20pregnant%20mothers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20diagnostic%20personnel%2C%20the%20team%20developed%20the%20Nirikhyana%20mobile%20application.%20This%20app%20facilitates%20effective%20information%20flow%20and%20real-time%20monitoring%2C%20vital%20for%20timely%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nearly%2042%20government%20and%20private%20clinics%20are%20offering%20up%20to%20three%20free%20ultrasound%20scans%20to%20pregnant%20women.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fodisha-ganjam-free-usgs-pregnant-women-3-1737031987-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-398461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENearly%2042%20government%20and%20private%20clinics%20are%20offering%20up%20to%20three%20free%20ultrasound%20scans%20to%20pregnant%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20backbone%20of%20this%20scheme%20is%20the%20Nirikhyana%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Berhampur%20Sub-Collector%20Dheenah%20Dastageer%20IAS%2C%20stressing%20its%20role%20in%20overcoming%20socioeconomic%20barriers%20and%20the%20digital%20divide.%20She%20also%20assisted%20the%20team%20in%20designing%20the%20mobile%20app%20and%20its%20implementation%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20follows%20a%20three-module%20approach%20that%20allows%20Auxiliary%20Nurse%20Midwives%20(ANMs)%20to%20register%20pregnant%20women%20on%20the%20Nirikhyana%20mobile%20app%2C%20facilitating%20consultations%20with%20doctors%20who%20can%20then%20refer%20cases%20to%20nearby%20ultrasound%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn